text: Motion

Tet-ten, teteten,
te-te-teten...!

──The part where you go "teteten".
This part.

Pyeh...! Was, was I off...?
Um──

It's okay.
C'mon. One, and.

Hmm～? Were you doing dance practice up here～?
Hinana wants to do it with Toru-senpai too～!
It's pretty hard.

Te-Ten, teteten,
Te-Te-Teten...

Toru-chan...
You sure are incredible, aren't you...?

...
You were doing just fine too, Koito.

E-Eheheh...
Of course, though! I can handle this much...!

And we've managed to get our very first work,
so we have to take it seriously...!
...You're right.

So, why did we take that job?

──Erm... the live show, I take it? I thought it was a
pretty good proposal. You've got reservations, then?

Indeed I do.
The values I hold are distinct from yours, after all.

...Everyone's brushed up their singing and dancing,
and I thought it was about time we had a concrete goal.

To make a large number of viewers notice you girls,
will surely be a hugely important experience, I think.

...Even though the ones to bear the full brunt
of this would be us, the merchandise.
I won't let you off, if anything is to happen.
